Question.Subject: how come my friends on aim say i randomly message them when i dont?
Question.Content: they always say that i send this 2 them, Tell me if you think I look hot in these pics they are on my profile Click Here.. Wtf is happening... occasionally it says that i have been signed on to aim from a different location
Question.ChosenAnswer: Sounds like maybe a spammer virus has hijacked your login information and sent it to a third party. Try to run a full system scan for viruses and change your login information.
